quizTitle: Can We Guess Your Deepest, Darkest Secret Based On What You See First?
quizDescription: What you see could reveal everything. . .

questionsArray.questionTitle: Finally, what do you see in this inkblot?

resultArray.resultTitle: You fear failure so much that you'll do anything to get ahead.
resultArray.resultDescription: You are deeply afraid of being a failure. You want to make something out of yourself, and hope to be successful in anything and everything you do. As a result, you are ruthlessly ambitious. You live in a cutthroat world, and you need to make sure you stay on top. If this means making some risky and borderline shady business deals, so be it. Because you are such a workhorse, you don't have a lot of time for your family and friends. You almost always put work before them. Take a moment out of your hectic day and call your family, they'd really love to hear from you!

resultArray.resultTitle: You are lying about your past.
resultArray.resultDescription: Shh...we won't tell anyone, but we know you're lying about who you are. You are not the person you say you are. Something happened in the past, and you've been keeping it a secret. You built a new identity and are living this whole new life. You're happy right now, but be careful, you're past might come back to haunt you when you least expect it.

At times, you feel like the world is swallowing you whole. You are crippled by anxiety and often feel very sad. When this happens, you doubt yourself and you're ability to be happy. You're unsure if life will get easier and things will get better. Sometimes you think there is no way out of this downward spiral. Stop keeping these low feelings to yourself. Even though you feel very lonely, you are surrounded by people who love you. Lean on them for help and you will feel better!
